{"word":"ἐπέρχομαι","slug":"ἐπέρχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐπέρχομαι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔρχομαι\">ἔρχομαι</a></el>] <b>come (on/upon)<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of moving over a space <b><a href='B:490 1:35'>Lk 1:35</a>; <a href='B:510 1:8'>Ac 1:8</a></b> (in both passages the Holy Spirit is viewed as coming from a transcendent realm); <b><a href='B:510 14:19'>14:19</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of an event or circumstance making its appearance <b><a href='B:560 2:7'>Eph 2:7</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on approaching peril <b><a href='B:490 11:22'>Lk 11:22</a>; <a href='B:490 21:26'>21:26</a>; <a href='B:510 8:24'>Ac 8:24</a>; <a href='B:510 13:40'>13:40</a>; <a href='B:660 5:1'>Js 5:1</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπεποίθει\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπερωτάω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}